element.text: After a 3-day free trial, your subscription will last for one month. With this auto-renewable subscription, you'll enjoy an ad-free experience, daily in-game bonuses and exclusive content to use in-game. Payment is charged to your +++ account. Subscription is renewed unless turned off at least 24 hours before the period ends and it can be turned off at any time in "account settings".
